        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I know of a method, but it wont work on dain, it only worked on summoning mobs that have low to moderate MR and your pet can tank (so this doesn't count to many summoning mobs). Make a pet, bring summoner, root summoner, keep it rooted... send pet, you wont be summoned because your pet will keep all agro this way.</P><P><font size=5><font color=red><b><center>Zeto</font id=red></b></center></font id=size5><BR><center>-Tholuxe Paells-</center><BR><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=125378" target="_blank">My Gear</a></center><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
